# Dea/L0 API Reference

Generated API reference for the Dea/L0 codebase.

This document is built from source comments and docstrings for:

- Stage 1 Python compiler sources under `compiler/stage1_py/`
- Stage 2 L0 compiler sources under `compiler/stage2_l0/src/`
- Shared L0 standard library modules under `compiler/shared/l0/stdlib/`
- Shared runtime headers under `compiler/shared/runtime/`

Design documents and project documentation are stored in the repository’s `docs` directory and are not duplicated in
this reference manual.

## About

- Project: Dea/L0, a small safe C-family systems language that compiles to C99.
- Source repository: [github.com/googlielmo/dea-lang-l0](https://github.com/googlielmo/dea-lang-l0).
- Created and maintained by `gwz` ([\@googlielmo](https://github.com/googlielmo)).

## Overview

This reference provides indexed access to the API by directory, namespace, class, and file. Detailed documentation for
each entity is provided in the corresponding sections.
